{{see|anne}}

==English==

===Etymology 1===
From the French ''[[#French|Anna]]'', from [[Hannah]].

===Proper noun===
'''Anne'''
# A female [[given name]].

===Etymology 2===
A shortened form of any of various Germanic masculine names which began with ''arn'' (''eagle'').

===Proper noun===
'''Anne'''
# A [[male]] [[given name]].

